{
    "poem_title": "- CVIII - ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "author": "Fcode Borja",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "Ahora es el tiempo cristalino Tormes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "que suenen tus acentos en tus cañas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "y adornada la frente de espadañas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "de Ninfas coros, agradables formes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ahora es el tiempo cristalino Tormes,\nque suenen tus acentos en tus cañas,\ny adornada la frente de espadañas,\nde Ninfas coros, agradables formes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Herido de sus pasos desconformes",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "el fértil suelo, que atrevido bañas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "respondan a sus ecos las montañas",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "con dulces voces, a tu amor conformes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Herido de sus pasos desconformes\nel fértil suelo, que atrevido bañas,\nrespondan a sus ecos las montañas\ncon dulces voces, a tu amor conformes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Enfrena de tu curso diligente",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "las presurosas aguas lisonjeras,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "que pasan de este sitio a su despecho.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Enfrena de tu curso diligente\nlas presurosas aguas lisonjeras,\nque pasan de este sitio a su despecho."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "Niega el tributo al mar osadamente,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "que si Filipo ilustra tus riberas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "libre te deja de tu antiguo pecho.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Niega el tributo al mar osadamente,\nque si Filipo ilustra tus riberas,\nlibre te deja de tu antiguo pecho."
        }
    ]
}